## ğŸ§© Best Practices

* âœ… Use **SSH keys** instead of passwords
* ğŸ” Restrict access to port **22** using NSG or Just-In-Time (JIT)
* ğŸ§¹ Organize resources with **Resource Groups and Tags**
* ğŸ’¾ Use **Managed Snapshots** for backups
* ğŸ’° Monitor costs when scaling up/down

